data.title: Galaxy Futures
data.meta_description:
Galaxy Futures | 727 followers on LinkedIn. Galaxy Futures Company is the first joint venture futures company approved by China Ministry of Commerce and China Securities Regulatory Commission.
 
      Galaxy Futures, holding largely by China Galaxy Securities funded by CIC (China Investment Corporation) and RBS, is evaluated as Class A for years. The current registered capital is RMB 1.2 billion.
